feed.title: RH Electronics DIY Geiger Counter Kit Monitoring
feed.description:
Online monitoring for nuclear radiation in Israel. Hardware used: MyGeiger DIY Kit with SBM-20 and Radiation Logger software.

Please visit store for circuit and DIY Geiger Kit for purchase.

What is the normal level?
For this tube CPM less than 60 indicates the normal background radiation level. 

All information presented as is. Radiation readings based on my DIY amateur project. I'm not represent any official statements. I'm not supply any warranty for radiation dose calculation accuracy.

This private Geiger Station not running for 24/7, but only when it available.
